Richard Wilson takes a journey into the past, following routes raved about in motoring guides of 50 years ago.

7. Richard Wilson Learns to Drive
In preparation for a motor journey, Richard is put through his paces as he learns how to use a gear stick again, having driven only automatics for the past 30 years. He drives classic cars, goes off-road, experiences the thrills and spills of the skidpan and gets a lesson in driving high performance cars from five-time Le Mans winner Derek Bell.
